ld/settle/question/answer/withhold/punctuate) and require every phrase to carry one. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-005 | Define Role enum (ostinato/melody/pad/perc/accent/silence) with grid_locked flag and role-filter policy used by all rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-006 | Implement seeded-RNG architecture with per-stage sub-seeds derived from a root seed along a seed_path tuple. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-007 | Refactor composition stage to emit score-tree with PerformanceIntent + SectionEnvelope + IntentTag metadata, deterministic from composition seed. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-008 | Define the OSC/SuperCollider event contract that carries full Event metadata including rule_stack provenance through to the synth. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-009 | Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-010 | Build a rule-ablation debugger that re-renders a score with selected rules disabled to localize expressive problems. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-011 | Build the RenderPass framework: ordered rule stack with stable order, per-rule enable flags, per-rule quantity k, and role-filter gating. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-012 | Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-013 | Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-014 | Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-015 | Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ±10%. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-01